{
  "name": "RPlog_Beers_Cheers_and_Buccaneers",
  "title": "Beers, Cheers and Buccaneers",
  "summary": "In the rowdy Beggar's Cove Cantina on Nar Shaddaa, the easygoing spacer Jaspar Andromidas settles in for a drink as the boisterous Rattataki pirate Shiari Vane swaggers in singing sea shanties with her crew, followed by the sharp-tongued pirate Nastaran Zohreh. Jaspar protests that he is merely a mover of exotic things, no pirate, but Vane and Nastaran take it upon themselves to school him in the pirate life -- get a fine coat, drink hard, and join a heist. They pitch him on participating in a job worth fifteen thousand credits for a few hours' work, with Vane leading the offer and Nastaran handling the seduction while a pesky monkey-lizard keeps stealing beers. Jaspar, curiosity piqued and never one to pass up work, agrees without need for Vane's threats of blasters. The deal sealed, the three toast to money, mission success, and many more adventures, Nastaran sputtering through her shot as the buccaneers cement their new partnership.",
